                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>\n                                        <date>23 November A<add>?</add> 5612</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I feel pleasure in <sic>transmiting</sic> to\n                                        you<lb/> the following resolutions unanimously passed this\n                                        day at a meeting<lb/> of the vestry (representatives of Kal\n                                        A Kodesh Beni Israel)<lb/> “Resolved. That the Holy\n                                        Congregation of the Children of Israel<lb/> thro' their\n                                        Vestry do hereby tender to the <persName>Revd Isaac\n                                                  Leeser</persName> of\n                                                  <placeName>Phila<lb/>=delphia</placeName> their\n                                        thanks for the intellectual and moral discourse\n                                        delivered<lb/> in their synagogue on the <date>sabbath of\n                                                  November 22<hi rend=\"sup\">nd</hi> 5612</date>\n                                        and<lb/> be it farther.</p>\n                              <p>Resolved That they hereby extend to the said gentleman a<lb/>\n                                        hearty welcome to <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>, and\n                                        feel happy in bearing addi<lb/>tional testimony to the high\n                                        attainments, <sic>accute</sic> knowledge<lb/> and moral\n                                        worth of the Revd gentleman.</p>\n                              <p>Resolved That we invite the <persName>Revd Mr Leeser</persName> to\n                                        address our<lb/> congregation on next <date>Sabbath</date>\n                                        if he should be amongst us<lb/> the shortness of notice at\n                                        which his discourse yesterday was de<lb/>=livered deprived\n                                        many of our community the pleasure of hear<lb/>ing him.</p>\n                              <p>Resolved That a copy of these resolutions be handed to\n                                                  <persName>Mr<lb/> Leeser</persName> and sent to\n                                        the “Asmonean” for publication and<lb/> that he be requested\n                                        to insert them in the next Occident.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(7)\">Respectfully yours</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\"><persName role=\"author\">Jos[ep]h\n                                                  Abraham</persName> Secy</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(4)\"><persName>D. Ullmann</persName> Parnas.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p33n21103/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
